### Register client successfully
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register/client
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Rodriguez",
  "birthday": "1995-05-12",
  "country": "Costa Rica",
  "bodyWeight": 68.5,
  "bodyMassIndex": 23.4,
  "waist": 74.2,
  "neck": 34.1,
  "hip": 96.7,
  "musclePercentage": 39.5,
  "fatPercentage": 24.8,
  "maxDailyCalories": 2100,
  "email": "maria.rodriguez@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

